OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FUnrelenting attacks by Iran on energy
OL,8,Finfrastructure and fuel tankers have
OL,9,Fpushed oil above the $100 a barrel
OL,10,Fmilestone once again, with no end to
OL,11,Fthe war in the Middle East in sight.
OL,13,FOil prices crossed the $100 mark on
OL,14,FMonday this week ` for the first time
OL,15,Fsince July 2022 ` before falling again
OL,16,Flater in the week after Donald Trump
OL,17,Fsuggested the war is "pretty much
OL,18,Fcomplete".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, the International Energy
OL,8,FAgency agreed to release 400 million
OL,9,Fbarrels of oil into global markets
OL,10,Ffrom reserves to soften the economic
OL,11,Fshock of the war.
OL,13,FIn response, Tehran has stepped up
OL,14,Fefforts to disrupt global energy
OL,15,Fsupplies, which pushed oil prices back
OL,16,Fup on Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FIran hit a container ship off the
OL,8,Fcoast of Dubai, caused a blaze near
OL,9,FBahrain's international airport,
OL,10,Ftargeted a major Saudi oil field with
OL,11,Fa drone attack and forced Iraq to halt
OL,12,Foperations at all the country's oil
OL,13,Fterminals after an attack on its port
OL,14,Fof Basra on the Persian Gulf.
OL,16,FLocal officials reported that the
OL,17,Fassault targeted vessels in a ship-to-
OL,18,Fship transfer of oil area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FIran flouted a United Nations Security
OL,8,FCouncil resolution from the previous
OL,9,Fday demanding that it halt strikes on
OL,10,Fits Gulf neighbours, with new attacks
OL,11,Falso reported in Kuwait and the United
OL,12,FArab Emirates.
OL,14,FSirens wailed before dawn in Jerusalem
OL,15,Fafter Israel said it was working to
OL,16,Fintercept missiles launched from Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FThe country also announced it had
OL,8,Fbegun a "wide-scale wave of strikes"
OL,9,Fon Tehran. In Lebanon, where Israel
OL,10,Fsays it is targeting Iran-linked
OL,11,FHezbollah militants, 11 people were
OL,12,Fkilled in two early morning strikes.
OL,14,FIn addition to attacking energy
OL,15,Finfrastructure around the region, Iran
OL,16,Fhas a stranglehold on the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz, the strategic waterway leading
OL,18,Ffrom the Persian Gulf toward the
OL,19,FIndian Ocean through which a fifth of
OL,20,Fthe world's oil is transported.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FWith traffic in the Strait effectively
OL,8,Fstopped, the price of Brent crude oil,
OL,9,Fan international benchmark for the oil
OL,10,Findustry, rose another 9% on Thursday
OL,11,Fto more than $100 a barrel, up some
OL,12,F38% over what it cost when the war
OL,13,Fstarted.
OL,15,FIn response to the effective shutting
OL,16,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, Saudi Arabia,
OL,17,Fthe world's largest oil exporter, has
OL,18,Fto redirect its maritime trade to its
OL,19,Fwestern Red Sea ports to avoid the
OL,20,FStrait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FMany other Gulf nations have also seen
OL,8,Ftheir energy infrastructure attacked
OL,9,Fand have reduced their output.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, the UN Security Council
OL,12,Fvoted to approve a resolution
OL,13,Fdemanding a halt to Iran's "egregious
OL,14,Fattacks" on its Gulf neighbours, who
OL,15,Fare allied with the US, but Tehran has
OL,16,Fshown no signs of backing down.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
