PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FAs Thursday began, a container ship in
OL,8,Fthe Persian Gulf was hit with an
OL,9,F"unknown projectile" off the coast of
OL,10,FDubai, sparking a small fire,
OL,11,Faccording to the United Kingdom
OL,12,FMaritime Trade Operations Centre,
OL,13,Fwhich said the crew were safe.
OL,15,FIn Bahrain, an Iranian attack sparked
OL,16,Fa major fire on Muharraq Island, home
OL,17,Fto the country's international
OL,18,Fairport. The airport has jet fuel
OL,19,Ftanks, and other tanks in the area
OL,20,Fserve the kingdom's oil industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
