OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FKuwait's Defence Ministry said an
OL,8,FIranian drone smashed into a
OL,9,Fresidential building, injuring two
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FThe UAE said it had activated air
OL,13,Fdefences twice to protect Dubai from
OL,14,Fattacks, and firefighters extinguished
OL,15,Fa blaze at a tower in Dubai Creek
OL,16,FHarbour after a drone hit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
