CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FSaudi Arabia said it shot down a drone
OL,8,Ftargeting the diplomatic quarter of
OL,9,Fthe capital, Riyadh, and also reported
OL,10,Fdowning drones in the kingdom's east,
OL,11,Fincluding at least one trying to
OL,12,Ftarget its Shaybah oil field.
OL,14,FFollowing an attack on Iraq's Basra
OL,15,Fport on Wednesday that killed at least
OL,16,Fone person, officials said on Thursday
OL,17,Fthat operations were halted at all the
OL,18,Fcountry's oil terminals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
