CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FFarhan al-Fartousi, the director-
OL,8,Fgeneral of the General Company for
OL,9,FPorts of Iraq, said the attack
OL,10,Ftargeted a vessel in a ship-to-ship
OL,11,Ftransfer area of the Persian Gulf port.
OL,13,FUK Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,14,Fsaid the government will "step in" if
OL,15,Fcompanies exploit rising heating oil
OL,16,Fprices amid the Middle East conflict.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUvD@bO]
