OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FPrices have jumped after Iran launched
OL,8,Fretaliatory strikes following attacks
OL,9,Fby the US and Israel, pushing up
OL,10,Fenergy costs and sending home heating
OL,11,Foil bills soaring.
OL,13,FAhead of a visit to Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fon Thursday, Starmer acknowledged that
OL,15,F"global instability has real impacts
OL,16,Fon the lives of working people across
OL,17,Fthe UK".
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
