CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FHe said: "Let me be clear, we will not
OL,8,Ftolerate profiteering or unfair
OL,9,Fpractices. If companies fleece
OL,10,Fcustomers or rip them off, we will not
OL,11,Fhesitate to step in, and that includes
OL,12,Fon regulation."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
