OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FIt comes after Rachel Reeves admitted
OL,8,Fit was "certainly not good for the
OL,9,FBritish economy to have trade
OL,10,Fdisrupted" and signalled the
OL,11,Fgovernment may be willing to move on
OL,12,Fenergy prices if the conflict worsens.
OL,14,FAppearing before Parliament's Treasury
OL,15,FCommittee on Wednesday, the Chancellor
OL,16,Fsaid the Treasury was looking at "a
OL,17,Fnumber of scenarios" but added it
OL,18,Fwould be "unwise to speculate" on the
OL,19,Fongoing economic fallout of the Iran
OL,20,Fwar.
OL,26,@pD@HOUrD@JO]xD@bOUyD@TO]zD@JOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773338766
OL,3,COil price tops $100 a barrel again as
OL,4,CIran steps up attacks on energy
OL,5,Cfacilities
OL,7,FReeves told MPs: "It's certainly not
OL,8,Fgood for the British economy to have
OL,9,Ftrade disrupted, and especially when
OL,10,Fso much oil and gas comes from that
OL,11,Fpart of the world.
OL,13,F"But the best thing that we can do as
OL,14,Fa government is to seek to de-escalate
OL,15,Fthis conflict. The quicker we can de-
OL,16,Fescalate, the better it will be for
OL,17,Fall of those different economic
OL,18,Fvariables."
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
